                <p><strong>What our attendees said about the event</strong></p>
                <p>Following the event, we sent a survey to all of the attendees and were delighted to see more than 130 people responded with their feedback.</p>
                <p>Again, thanks to all of our attendees for their useful feedback and positive messages that we received. The positive feedback means we will be able to focus on what you enjoyed at the event, so we can incorporate it into our planning for
                    next year&rsquo;s event, along with some lessons learnt from this year.</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
